{"tid":941060,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大塚愛離婚後首度公開亮相《FNS歌謠祭》  自彈自唱《星象儀》","createTime":"2018-12-14T12:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T07:07:05.000Z","uid":9573,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7329c802551200115ec9676077a2c3492f891a7e","tid":941060,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"日本富士電視台大型直播音樂騷《FNS歌謠祭》一分為二舉行，昨日舉行「第2夜」演出。演出歌手單位包括星野源、E-girls、Kis-My-Ft2、King &amp; Prince、金在中、城田優、Sexy Zone、DEAN FUJIOKA、AKB48、IZ*ONE、櫸坂46及乃木坂46等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181213/photo/bkn-20181213121154374-1213_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181213124244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181213121154374-1213_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181213124244&h=f8ceffb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大塚愛離婚後，首度亮相直播音樂騷演唱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181213/photo/bkn-20181213121154374-1213_00862_001_02p.jpg?20181213124244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181213121154374-1213_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20181213124244&h=a0d0569b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她自彈自唱名曲《星象儀》，期間唱錯歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n剛與組合RIP SLYME成員老公SU結束8年婚姻的女歌手大塚愛，離婚後首度亮相演出。她彈鋼琴演唱其代表名曲《星象儀》，期間未知是否太緊張而唱錯歌詞，騷後她在社交網鞠躬道歉的相片，獲網民大讚可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.news.livedoor.com/newsimage/stf/9/3/93c64_1628_9c941b1d_1917bdde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.news.livedoor.com%2Fnewsimage%2Fstf%2F9%2F3%2F93c64_1628_9c941b1d_1917bdde.jpg&h=3154cba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n騷後她在社交網鞠躬道歉的相片，獲網民大讚可愛。<br />\n<br />\n而韓國選秀節目《Produce 48》出身的限定女團IZONE，與AKB48、乃木坂46、櫸坂46同台，演唱由監製秋元康只此一晚為節目炮製的歌曲《必然性》。節目平均收視較去年上升有11.8%，瞬間最高收視有14.9%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7tDEC6bPQ28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7tDEC6bPQ28&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncm7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=80f41067\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7tDEC6bPQ28</a><br />\n大塚愛「プラネタリウム」FNS歌謡祭2018"},{"pid":"67eea070a8e6752f83fa602ec93a5801a477fde7","tid":941060,"uid":73404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本全部唱得歌既女當年都結晒婚<br />\n如果唔係咁kpop都無可能會彈得起<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年個個離晒婚又出番黎唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17577c7c7fd1259bc4c628224ba7a6601254ed38","tid":941060,"uid":47027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"67eea070a8e6752f83fa602ec93a5801a477fde7","tid":941060,"uid":73404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本全部唱得歌既女當年都結晒婚<br />\n如果唔係咁kpop都無可能會彈得起<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年個個離晒婚又出番黎唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"幾時到YUI?"},{"pid":"049beaaa7ebe11cad52de229617b0f2227a95b55","tid":941060,"uid":138065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"冇亂入嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5604f8f8ad7bb690b60676909505fe40748235","tid":941060,"uid":34395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca6ae11ae97d156f4ffd5917ec7fdaa6085eaba","tid":941060,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae1e99866ce48b59bed1a6368d25a44e5c7d304","tid":941060,"uid":73412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,